race.comment: Tactical and they're racing on a heavy track. SETHEUS (4) found one much too good at Warrnambool but ran a good number at Sale prior. Suited and he's a decent chance to go one better. LEFT HOOK (3) is an improver in a top metro yard. Will enjoy the longer sprint and has been kept on the fresh side. Has more to offer.  BANXI (1) resumes and has placed in two Flemington jumpouts. He's much better than the form line suggests and deserves a close betting watch. TESTY NIC (6) has been freshened and he's raced well enough in both his race starts. He also deserves plenty of consideration in a tricky race.
